headline: Principal® Appoints Lisa Coulson to Lead Human Resources
summary: DES MOINES, Iowa, November 25, 2024--Principal Financial Group® (Nasdaq: PFG) today announced Lisa Coulson as the company’s next chief human resources officer and senior vice president, effective Nov. 30, 2024. Coulson steps into the role after 17 years with Principal and significant experience helping companies align talent strategy with business objectives and customer needs.
